WEBVTT

00:11:29.560 --> 00:11:32.296
That was an amazing day,

00:11:32.320 --> 00:11:35.800
and the House and Senate passed the ADA.

00:11:36.520 --> 00:11:41.976
And then President Bush signed the ADA.

00:11:42.000 --> 00:11:43.576
It's a great picture.

00:11:43.600 --> 00:11:47.656
President Bush signed the ADA
on the lawn of the White House.

00:11:47.680 --> 00:11:49.656
It was an amazing day,

00:11:49.680 --> 00:11:52.200
and there are about 2,000 people there.

00:11:53.000 --> 00:11:56.960
It was July 26, 1990.

00:11:57.720 --> 00:12:01.416
And one of the most famous
statements he had in his speech